                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner at No. 1, Little Exeter-street; he appeared to be asleep - I said "You appear very fast asleep?" he opened his eyes, and said "I did not take the bacon. it was another boy."</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I said I knew nothing about it.</p>
